# pushfeed

Simple API allowing presenters and observers to connect.

## Presenters Collection [/presenters]

### List all presenters [GET /presenters]

+ Response 200 (application/json)

        [
          {
            "id": 1,
            "created_at": "2016-01-16T20:21:58.694Z",
