### Create a presenter [POST]

+ Request (application/json)

+ Response 201 (application/json)

    + Body

            {
              "id": 1,
              "created_at": "2016-01-16T20:21:58.694Z",
              "updated_at": "2016-01-16T20:21:58.694Z"
            }

### Delete a presenter [DELETE /presenters/{id}]

+ Response 204 (application/json)


